                </svg>
                <span class="text-footer text-color">The product is developed since 18/10/2023</span>
            </p>
            <p class="p-footer text-color">
                Developed by group 2TN2T
            </p>
            <p class="p-footer text-color">
                -Project Social Network-
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>

</body>
</html>
